
// This Hyperlambda code checks if a node named [case] has a value of "decimal" and then sets the value of the [type] node, which is a child of the [schema] node, to "number". The [set-value] slot is used to change the value of the target node specified by the expression.
case:decimal
   set-value:x:@.arg/*/schema/*/type
      .:number
